msgid ""
"The Elementals are the guardians of the World, spirits of the elements that "
"incarnate themselves to fight. They are reclusive, but can be quite fierce "
"and brutal, for as it is said, there is nothing more ruthless than nature."
msgstr ""
"Les Élémentaires sont les gardiens du Monde, des esprits des éléments qui "
"s'incarnent pour combattre. Ils sont reclus, mais peuvent devenir féroces et "
"brutaux, car comme l'on dit, il n'y a rien de plus impitoyable que la nature."

